Suggests he may have had a speech impediment.

TITLE EVIDENCE:
December 1989 photo caption: "M Augusto Januário and M Gaguinho Preto"
The "M" prefix confirms recognition as Mestre before 2002 death.
Photo from Omilad D''Angola''s collection.

TEACHERS:
