- Mestre Daniel Canedo (born 1961, trained mid-1970s to late 1980s)

LINEAGE:
Neném → Paizinho (Teodoro Ramos) → Artur Emídio → Paulo Gomes → Josias da Silva

GROUPS FOUNDED:
