STUDENTS:
- Mestre Dom Ivan (Ivan Zacarias Guimarães Gobbo) - received mestre title from Onça Tigre; documented in photographs
- Mestre Baleado (Risomar Torres Arruda) - associated with Onça Tigre''s lineage in Brasília
- Numerous students at CPOR academy who became political leaders

FAMILY:
- Parents: Joaquim Carvalho Sobrinho and Maria Freire de Carvalho
- Nephew: Julival do Espírito Santo (Mestre Gato de Silvestre) - first contact with capoeira through Onça Tigre in Goiás

ORGANIZATIONS FOUNDED/LED:
- Grupo de Capoeira Meia Lua (May 29, 1962) - founding date documented
- AscaDF (Associação de Capoeira do DF) - served as President
