RELATIONSHIP TO POLOCA:
Paulo Barreto (Mestre Poloca) shares the same surname "Barreto" but no source explicitly confirms they are siblings. They are fellow co-founders of Nzinga and both were at GCAP from its founding. Both are described as disciples of Moraes, João Grande, and Cobra Mansa. The relationship (if any) is unconfirmed.

